      h5#selected_expiry
        | Select a Date and Time...
      i#flatpckr.md-button--circle.md-button--48.cui-icon.icon.icon-calendar-month_36(style='color:#000000')
      p
      br
      button#create_button.cui-button
        | Create Session
    section
      div
        br
        p#messages
    section#send_as_email_section.dreams(style='display:none;')
      br
      button#reload_button.cui-button(onclick='window.location.reload();')
        | Create Another Session
